    <item>
      <title>墨西哥的 Sheinbaum 决定留任 AMLO 的财政部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/mexico-s-sheinbaum-decides-to-keep-amlo-s-finance-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥当选总统克劳迪娅·辛鲍姆周一证实，财政部长罗赫里奥·拉米雷斯·德拉奥同意在其政府任期内继续担任现任职务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/mexico-s-sheinbaum-decides-to-keep-amlo-s-finance-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 23:53:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚军方因缺口加大而招募外国人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/australia-s-military-to-recruit-foreigners-as-shortfall-deepens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚军方正在放宽招募标准，允许非公民加入军队，并帮助解决国防军人员短缺的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/australia-s-military-to-recruit-foreigners-as-shortfall-deepens</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 23:24:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登和美墨边境危机在 Sheinbaum 的早期任期内愈演愈烈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/biden-border-crisis-loom-large-in-sheinbaum-s-early-hours</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克劳迪娅·希因鲍姆 (Claudia Sheinbaum) 只享受了几个小时的胜利，她将成为墨西哥第一位女总统，但她的北方邻居就提醒她，新的工作有多么困难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/biden-border-crisis-loom-large-in-sheinbaum-s-early-hours</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 23:20:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>企业敦促下一届英国政府减少脱欧贸易摩擦</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/business-urges-next-uk-government-to-cut-brexit-trade-friction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国工业联合会敦促下一届英国政府缓解贸易摩擦以促进经济增长，这使得英国脱欧后与欧盟的关系成为焦点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/business-urges-next-uk-government-to-cut-brexit-trade-friction</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将于 10 月 4 日上诉佐治亚州，选举前审判将以失败告终</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/trump-georgia-appeal-set-for-oct-4-dooming-pre-election-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 要求将富尔顿县地方检察官法尼·威利斯 (Fani Willis) 调离佐治亚州选举干预案的上诉，审理时间暂定于 10 月 4 日，这使得在 11 月 5 日美国总统大选之前进行审判几乎不可能。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/trump-georgia-appeal-set-for-oct-4-dooming-pre-election-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 22:16:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍勃·梅内德斯在受审期间申请以独立人士身份竞选参议员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/new-jersey-s-menendez-files-to-run-as-independent-while-on-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新泽西州民主党人鲍勃·梅嫩德斯周一申请以独立候选人身份竞选连任，对于试图保住安全参议院席位的民主党人来说，此举可能会付出高昂代价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/new-jersey-s-menendez-files-to-run-as-independent-while-on-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 22:00:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克与斯塔默首次辩论之际，奈杰尔·法拉奇全力投入英国竞选活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/farage-says-he-ll-stand-in-uk-election-in-blow-to-sunak-s-tories</link>
      <description><![CDATA[奈杰尔·法拉奇的批评者称他为“无耻的机会主义者”。周一，这位脱欧设计者选择了一个完美的时机给里希·苏纳克一记重拳——英国大选首场电视辩论的前一天，而一项重要民意调查显示，首相领导的执政党保守党将遭遇历史性溃败。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/farage-says-he-ll-stand-in-uk-election-in-blow-to-sunak-s-tories</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 15:22:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>天安门事件三十五周年纪念日前夕，香港拘捕多名艺术家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-03/hong-kong-detains-an-artist-on-the-eve-of-the-35th-anniversary-of-china-s-tiananmen-square-crackdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港（美联社）——在中国天安门广场镇压 35 周年前夕，香港警方短暂拘留了一名行为艺术家，凸显了这座城市的言论自由正在萎缩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-03/hong-kong-detains-an-artist-on-the-eve-of-the-35th-anniversary-of-china-s-tiananmen-square-crackdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 15:09:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列称除非哈马斯被摧毁，否则不会永久停火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/israel-says-biden-s-latest-gaza-peace-plan-is-only-part-of-story</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡重申，在该国提出的条件得到满足（包括消灭该激进组织）之前，加沙对哈马斯的战争不会永久停火。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/israel-says-biden-s-latest-gaza-peace-plan-is-only-part-of-story</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 14:54:03 GMT</pubDate>
